#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:2
msgid "RMI"
msgstr "RMI"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:6
msgid ""
"RMI(Remote Method "
"Invocation，远程方法调用)能够让在客户端Java虚拟机上的对象像调用本地对象一样调用服务端Java虚拟机中的对象上的方法。其中RMI标准实现是Java"
" RMI，之外还有Weblogic RMI、Spring RMI等不同的实现。"
msgstr ""
"RMI (Remote Method Invocation) allows an object in a client-side Java "
"virtual machine to call methods on an object in a server-side Java virtual "
"machine as if it were calling a local object. The standard RMI "
"implementation is Java RMI, and other implementations include WebLogic RMI "
"and Spring RMI."

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:8
msgid "RMI中比较重要的两个概念是Stub和Skeleton，Stub和Skeleton对同一套接口进行实现，其中Stub由Client端调用，并不进行真正的实现，而是和Server端通信。Skeleton是Server端，监听来自Stub的连接，根据Stub发送的数据进行真正的操作。"
msgstr "Two important concepts in RMI are Stub and Skeleton. Stub and Skeleton implement the same interface set. The Stub is called by the Client side; it does not perform the actual implementation, but communicates with the Server side. The Skeleton is on the Server side, listens for connections from the Stub, and performs the real operation based on the data sent by the Stub."

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:11
msgid "调用步骤"
msgstr "Call Steps"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:12
msgid "客户调用客户端辅助对象Stub上的方法"
msgstr "The client calls a method on the client helper object Stub"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:13
msgid "客户端辅助对象Stub打包调用信息(变量，方法名)，通过网络发送给服务端辅助对象Skeleton"
msgstr "The client helper object Stub packages the call information, including variables and method name, and sends it over the network to the server helper object Skeleton"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:14
msgid "服务端辅助对象Skeleton将客户端辅助对象发送来的信息解包，找出真正被调用的方法以及该方法所在对象"
msgstr "The server helper object Skeleton unpacks the information sent by the client helper object and identifies the real method being called and the object that owns it"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:15
msgid "调用真正服务对象上的真正方法，并将结果返回给服务端辅助对象Skeleton"
msgstr "It calls the real method on the real service object and returns the result to the server helper object Skeleton"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:16
msgid "服务端辅助对象将结果打包，发送给客户端辅助对象Stub"
msgstr "The server helper object packages the result and sends it to the client helper object Stub"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:17
msgid "客户端辅助对象将返回值解包，返回给调用者"
msgstr "The client helper object unpacks the return value and returns it to the caller"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:18
msgid "客户获得返回值"
msgstr "The client receives the return value"

