#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:164
msgid "T3协议"
msgstr "T3 Protocol"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:165
msgid "T3协议是用于在WebLogic服务器和其他类型的Java程序之间传输信息的协议，是Weblogic对RMI规范的实现。简单来说，可以把T3视为暴露JDNI给用户调用的接口。"
msgstr "The T3 protocol is used to transmit information between WebLogic servers and other types of Java programs. It is WebLogic's implementation of the RMI specification. In simple terms, T3 can be viewed as an interface that exposes JNDI for user calls."

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:168
msgid "JRMP"
msgstr "JRMP"

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:169
msgid ""
"Java远程方法协议(Java Remote Method "
"Protocol，JRMP)是特定于Java技术的、用于查找和引用远程对象的协议。这是运行在Java远程方法调用(RMI)之下、TCP/IP之上的线路层协议。"
msgstr ""
"Java Remote Method Protocol (JRMP) is a Java-technology-specific protocol "
"used to locate and reference remote objects. It is a wire-level protocol "
"that runs below Java Remote Method Invocation (RMI) and above TCP/IP."

#: ../../source/language/java/rmi.rst:171
msgid "JRMP是一个Java特有的、适用于Java之间远程调用的基于流的协议，要求客户端和服务器上都使用Java对象。"
msgstr "JRMP is a Java-specific stream-based protocol for remote calls between Java systems, and it requires Java objects on both the client and server."
